  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081200/extras/5bab724a31491b110daac4b49b4aabec.avif?t=1711563037\" width=591 height=86 /></span><br><br>It wasn't very famous, but it's been mentioned a lot recently.<br><br>It didn't seem like anything compared to all the rumors, but they realize that no one was filming a video at night in this haunted house.<br><br>They hope be the first record video came to ghost house tonight.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Haunted:Live is a single player psychological horror game.</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >you need for search and inspect on the quiet place alone to runaway from demonic symptom encount.</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >you can use for investigation method like PC, Book, Paper, demonic object to get hint and find unlock door, defeat demonic symptom. </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay</strong></h2><br><strong>Search & Inspect</strong><br>You will explore the old ruins and face the records you can find there<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081200/extras/49fe8946df821c4a8532985fab161df8.poster.avif?t=1711563037\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081200/extras/49fe8946df821c4a8532985fab161df8.webm?t=1711563037\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081200/extras/49fe8946df821c4a8532985fab161df8.mp4?t=1711563037\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081200/extras/3e8db6fcb058d305a654e4a8837c43c0.avif?t=1711563037\" width=700 height=356 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081200/extras/33c103b928a102a02592ae6582960ae2.avif?t=1711563037\" width=700 height=356 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081200/extras/51e7b368139d494566f84ccd68c7e4bf.avif?t=1711563037\" width=700 height=356 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081200/extras/6c3db7f4759a3af652228d71c6d9218e.avif?t=1711563037\" width=700 height=356 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081200/extras/caaf1e5a10a6dacf7da732ef0730801f.avif?t=1711563037\" width=700 height=356 /></span><br><br><br><br><br><strong>Inventory & Journal</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081200/extras/a091e07502806b35646fea590dd47553.avif?t=1711563037\" width=700 height=356 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081200/extras/d8d4e4bbc68db04f4a3b65a3d4796e60.avif?t=1711563037\" width=700 height=356 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081200/extras/f8e03234940f3dd5e1910e2c21e434d0.avif?t=1711563037\" width=700 height=356 /></span><br><br><br><strong>Save & Load / Checkpoint</strong><br><br>You can Save and Load Game<br>if player reached checkpoint Game will be automaticaly save.<br><br><br><strong>Multiple Endings / Collected Endinglist</strong><br>9 Branched Ending<br>Once you finish the game, you can watch Collected Endinglist/Epilogue from Mainmenu<br><br><br><br><strong>Xbox One Controller Support</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akam